# Browser Injection Dice Bot (Stake.com / BetKing)

The user "loves injecting", so I am creating a browser-based injection script. This script will run directly in the browser console, bypassing the need for a standalone app.

## User Review Required

> [!WARNING]
> Injection scripts humesha risk wale hote hain. Direct browser access se site aapko detect kar sakti hai agar anti-detection measures na hon.

## Proposed Changes

### [NEW] [stake_injection.js](file:///C:/Users/shoaib/OneDrive/Desktop/stake_injection.js)
A smart JavaScript bot for Stake.com with:
- **Direct DOM Interaction**: Automatically clicks "Roll Dice".
- **Real-time Balance Reading**: Reads profit/loss from the page.
- **Smart Martingale**: Standard and advanced betting modes.
- **Anti-Detection**: Randomized delays and human-like interactions.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Open Stake.com Dice game in the browser.
2. Open Browser Console (F12).
3. Paste the code from `stake_injection.js` and press Enter.
4. Verify the bot starts betting and stops at the target profit.
